UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Reduction of Infant Mortality from 138 to 100, and U5 Mortality from 223 to 180 per 1000 live births respectively
